514
00:41:23.496 --> 00:41:25.163
For you to die, old fart!

515
00:41:27.996 --> 00:41:29.996
Rascal! Scoundrel!

516
00:41:30.205 --> 00:41:32.496
Get out!

517
00:41:32.580 --> 00:41:34.621
I'll break your legs, you swine.

518
00:41:37.038 --> 00:41:41.413
