631
00:49:30.913 --> 00:49:32.330
Mary Poppins.

632
00:49:32.455 --> 00:49:35.371
Sanju knows. You have no clue.

633
00:49:35.913 --> 00:49:37.288
Ruby, 4 p.m. tomorrow.

634
00:49:37.705 --> 00:49:39.830
The Marriage Registrar's office.

