00:55:56.538 --> 00:55:57.455
What happened?

704
00:55:58.871 --> 00:56:01.163
She slipped into a coma again.

705
00:56:01.246 --> 00:56:04.996
-I just met her yesterday!
-No, day before.


706
00:56:05.080 --> 00:56:08.913
You've woken up after two days. It's okay.

707
00:56:13.246 --> 00:56:15.038
I've spoken to the doctors.

708
