No!

711
00:56:21.455 --> 00:56:22.955
Please don't send me there, Dad.

712
00:56:23.121 --> 00:56:24.830
Just a few days, sonny.

713
00:56:25.330 --> 00:56:26.496
No.

714
00:56:30.788 --> 00:56:34.205
Come out. We won't send you anywhere.

715
00:56:34.288 --> 00:56:37.121
I had one cigarette, you packed me off
to boarding school.


716
00:56:37.205 --> 00:56:40.038
I was just six.
Couldn't even tie my shoelaces.


717
00:56:40.121 --> 00:56:41.413
I missed mom.

718
00:56:43.330 --> 00:56:44.246
Please come out.

719
00:56:45.496 --> 00:56:47.288
I won't go anywhere.

720
00:56:47.580 --> 00:56:50.080
