722
00:56:58.205 --> 00:57:01.496
That I wouldn't do drugs in the hospital.

723
00:57:01.788 --> 00:57:03.205
And I promised.

724
00:57:03.830 --> 00:57:06.246
I started spending
every night at the hospital.


725
00:57:06.746 --> 00:57:09.371
