751
01:00:36.163 --> 01:00:37.413
Sanju.

752
01:00:46.038 --> 01:00:47.205
What happened?

753
01:00:48.455 --> 01:00:51.038
Mom opened her eyes before she died.

754
01:00:51.996 --> 01:00:55.288
She touched my head to bless me.

755
01:00:59.371 --> 01:01:02.496
Not sure if it happened
or I was hallucinating...


756
01:01:03.163 --> 01:01:04.955
I'm a mess, Dad.

757
01:01:05.246 --> 01:01:08.413
I can't tell what's real
and what's imaginary.


758
01:01:11.788 --> 01:01:13.038
Are you real, Dad?

759
01:01:15.705 --> 01:01:16.830
Buddy, listen.

760
01:01:16.996 --> 01:01:18.830
Is that Mr. Sunil Dutt?

761
01:01:19.580 --> 01:01:21.996
-Is dad there?
-Yes.


762
01:01:23.996 --> 01:01:25.288
Please save me, Dad.

763
01:01:25.455 --> 01:01:26.621
I want to quit drugs.

764
01:01:26.788 --> 01:01:28.246
I want to live.

765
01:01:32.455 --> 01:01:35.580
You'll be fine, sonny.

766
01:01:42.163 --> 01:01:44.038
