Howdy, Yerwada!

1691
02:20:31.205 --> 02:20:35.288
This is your buddy, Sanju!

1692
02:20:38.788 --> 02:20:41.746
Today's topic is "friendship."

1693
02:20:42.163 --> 02:20:44.288
My best friend was Kamli.

1694
02:20:45.205 --> 02:20:49.121
Great guy. But fell prey to drugs.

1695
02:20:49.996 --> 02:20:52.913
No... not the psychotropic drugs.

1696
02:20:53.330 --> 02:20:59.913
But the ones that are slid
under our doors, daily.


1697
02:21:00.746 --> 02:21:02.913
We have them with our morning tea.

1698
02:21:03.413 --> 02:21:06.746
Drugs called "News."

1699
02:21:07.621 --> 02:21:09.413
