1706
02:21:34.580 --> 02:21:38.246
No cop, no prosecutor,
no witness ever said


1707
02:21:38.330 --> 02:21:40.455
there was a truck
with RDX at my house.

1708
02:21:41.080 --> 02:21:42.246
So, why this headline?

1709
02:21:42.580 --> 02:21:47.538
