the bomb blast conspiracy.


1726
02:23:02.330 --> 02:23:04.705
Kamlesh, please wait outside.

1727
02:23:09.080 --> 02:23:12.996
-I knew nothing about the bomb blasts.
-But tell the Court that you knew.


1728
02:23:13.371 --> 02:23:16.371
Tell them who got the RDX,
who made the bombs,


1729
02:23:16.788 --> 02:23:18.163
and who planted them.

1730
02:23:18.246 --> 02:23:22.163
-I know nothing!
-I'll give you the names.


1731
02:23:22.496 --> 02:23:25.705
