will make it the truth.

1735
02:23:39.163 --> 02:23:41.288
The country will spit on me.

1736
02:23:42.121 --> 02:23:43.580
Leave the country.

1737
02:23:43.913 --> 02:23:45.496
London, Kenya... Pick a place.

1738
02:23:46.663 --> 02:23:51.621
And dad? My sisters? 
Dad, heard that?

1739
02:23:51.705 --> 02:23:54.996
Don't worry about us. 
Leave the country.

1740
02:24:00.746 --> 02:24:04.371
Sir, I don't have a law degree.

1741
02:24:05.121 --> 02:24:06.955
In fact, I'm a college dropout.

1742
02:24:07.205 --> 02:24:10.163
But I know, this is rotten advice.

1743
02:24:10.830 --> 02:24:14.038
