and run away?


1744
02:24:14.663 --> 02:24:16.288
People will hate dad.

1745
02:24:16.496 --> 02:24:19.913
His life's work, respect...
All down the drain!


1746
02:24:19.996 --> 02:24:22.496
-Listen to me...
-You listen to me.


1747
02:24:22.580 --> 02:24:25.830
Get lost!
You might be a great lawyer,


1748
02:24:25.913 --> 02:24:29.621
but with a broken nose,
you'll look like a clown.


1749
02:24:36.538 --> 02:24:39.038
You're going to pay for this.

1750
02:24:53.538 --> 02:24:54.705
What happened, Dad?

1751
02:24:56.038 --> 02:24:57.455
Ace, sonny!

1752
02:25:07.371 --> 02:25:09.955
