I turned villain for my friend.


1755
02:25:18.371 --> 02:25:22.413
Hey, Kamli. Hope you can hear me.

1756
02:25:23.955 --> 02:25:25.538
When I come out...

1757
02:25:27.330 --> 02:25:29.121
meet me once, buddy.

1758
02:25:30.913 --> 02:25:32.705
If you do, I'll be happy.

1759
02:25:34.413 --> 02:25:37.830
